Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.00,0:11:57.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Proč jsi nervozní  Misa?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.18,0:12:03.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ijima!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.00,0:12:14.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Co?
